*Slučajnost* je postala deo naše svakodnevnice. (Chance has become part of our everyday life.) 

Mnogo je *slučajnosti* u našim životima. (There is a lot of chance in our lives.)

Mogućnost da se dogodi *slučajnost* je veoma velika. (The possibility of a chance occurence is very big.)

Događaji koji se smatraju *slučajnim* su često veoma značajni. (Events that are considered random are often very significant.)

Neke stvari se događaju samo zbog *slučajnosti*. (Some things happen just by chance.)